# SacredSDK .gitignore
#
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Current push surface: docs/ + tools/
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Documentation under docs/ and the Python toolchain under tools/ are
# public. The C++ DLL implementation (and vendored third-party C++)
# stays held back until the public API surface stabilises.
#
# Strategy: deny-by-default at sdk/ root, allow-list specific
# subdirectories below.

# ─── deny-by-default in sdk/ root ───────────────────────────────────────
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/LICENSE
!/docs/
!/tools/

# ─── docs/ — allow only top-level .md ──────────────────────────────────
docs/*
!docs/*.md

# Internal handoff doc — agent-to-agent context, not for public eyes.
# Held back even though it's an .md.
docs/HANDOFF.md

# ─── tools/ — allow .py / .csv / .bat / .md / ghidra scripts ───────────
tools/*
!tools/*.md
!tools/*.py
!tools/*.csv
!tools/*.bat
!tools/ghidra/
tools/ghidra/*
!tools/ghidra/*.java
!tools/ghidra/*.bat
!tools/ghidra/*.md

# Scratch is one-off recon scripts from earlier RE sessions; kept
# locally for archaeology but not part of the public surface.
tools/scratch/

# Ghidra-derived decompiled C from Sacred.exe — keep local only.
# Modders don't need it; RE hackers can regenerate from Sacred.exe
# + the Java scripts in tools/ghidra/.
tools/ghidra/decompiled/

# ─── safety nets for things we never want anywhere ─────────────────────
# (These mostly belong above already via the deny-by-default at /*, but
# spell them out so a future loosening of the whitelist doesn't
# accidentally start tracking them.)

# Build artifacts
Release/
Debug/
x64/
*.obj
*.pdb
*.exp
*.ilk
*.lib
*.dll
*.exe
*.bin

# Vendored third-party
imgui/
lua/

# Runtime-decrypted Sacred.exe dump — derived data, not redistributable.
Sacred_decrypted.exe
*.exe.bak

# Logs / per-run dumps
logs/
*.log
*.trace
*.dmp

# Ghidra working dirs
ghidra/
*.gpr
*.rep
*.lock~

# IDE / editor cruft
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
**/.idea/
.idea.*/
*.user
*.opensdf
*.sdf
*.suo
*.sln.docstates

# Python build/cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.pytest_cache/

# OS noise
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
Desktop.ini
